HEADWORD: Geoselenic
<hw>Ge`o*se*len"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>ge`a</grk>, <grk>gh^</grk>, the earth + <?/ moon.]</ety>
